title: Biggest NFL Draft Surprises, Game of Thrones Episode 2 (Football 4/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the latest draft buzz around the top picks, to examine what surprises might happen and then to recap Game of Thrones Season 8, Episode 2.
